title: Trump Threatens Canada With 50% Tariff On Aircraft Sold In US, Expanding Trade War
summary_full: President Donald Trump on Thursday threatened Canada with a 50% tariff on any aircraft sold in the US, the latest salvo in his trade war with America's northern neighbor as his feud with Prime Minister Mark Carney expands.
